  </header>

  <section class="support-container">
    <h1>Need Help with Dairify?</h1>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="faq-section">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>How do I set up the machine?</strong><br />The setup is automatic and guided by the screen. Just plug and start.</li>
        <li><strong>What does the machine detect?</strong><br />It detects common antibiotics like Penicillin and Tetracycline.</li>
        <li><strong>Can I use my own enzymes?</strong><br />Yes, the machine allows for enzyme input and tracking.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

